headline: DexCom Stock Falls Despite Q4 Earnings Beat, G7 Rollout Drives Growth
summary: DXCM beats Q4 EPS estimates, posts 13% revenue growth and reiterates 2026 guidance as G7 15 Day rollout and margin gains drive momentum.

headline: Will ISRG's R&D Focus Following Solid Earnings Growth Drive Demand?
summary: Intuitive Surgical balances 22% EPS growth with heavier 2026 R&D and expansion spending, betting near-term margin pressure will fuel long-term demand.
